{"id": 3009, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都习惯了哪些日常中的“碎片化”？", "description": "不知不觉，在当代生活中，边界清晰的东西似乎越来越少，微小而难以形容的“碎片”反而越来越多了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 10605, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190924223940QiJrzK6XGWsfwjkF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-24T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5936, "title": "你都习惯了哪些日常中的“碎片化”？", "content": "你都习惯了哪些日常中的“碎片化”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347263, "content": "时间碎片化，通勤/工作/休闲时间没有明确的界限", "image": "img/option/option/20190924213605LTOZB1uU4gkDJnPW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347264, "content": "注意力碎片化，很少有专心做一件事情的时刻", "image": "img/option/option/201909242138299HgonLpW1iaZ4Dlw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347265, "content": "情绪碎片化，日常充满各种小确幸、小确烦、小确丧", "image": "img/option/option/20190924214152kZNKhwAICUeYHT5E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347266, "content": "知识碎片化，随时能 get 一些“并没有啥用”的今日新知", "image": "img/option/option/201909242144298IXJf2pkmsUbLNtK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347267, "content": "信息碎片化，信息长期超载但真正记得住的却很少", "image": "img/option/option/20190924215300aumBLfSO1D4drIVR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347269, "content": "社交碎片化，点赞之交/砍价之交…线上线下各司其职", "image": "img/option/option/20190924220130cATHwt8OdISrWNFp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347270, "content": "流行碎片化，垂直的“小范围爱好圈”越来越多", "image": "img/option/option/20190924221857vy6eOiGNQtfTobmq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347272, "content": "表达碎片化，习惯用“喜不喜欢”的简单态度代替复杂事实", "image": "img/option/option/20190924223605io21FrZ0xCmcNqXW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}